CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 9, 1963, pg. 4, reads: "Fireside Chat - This knit outfit, black slacks and green, loose-fitted, sleeveless blouse, worn by sleek Marlene Thomas, is just the thing for chatting by the fire. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Marlene Thomas wearing dark pants and light colored sleeveless knitted v-neck sweater with dark trim, standing in Holiday House for D. I. Club annual MENDS benefit
